reviewText: Very happy. Have been trying to get this in Australia, but amazon did it for me. Thanks

A 1955 FILM ABOUT AN ABORIGINAL GIRL BROUGHT UP BY A WHITE AUSSIE WOMAN....A LOT OF FABULOUS SCENERY FROM THE NORTHERN TERRITORIES..THIS FILM IS A REAL LEARNING EXPERIENCE IN TERMS OF LEARNING ABOUT THE ABORIGINES AND THE LAND OF THE NW TERRITORIES
